          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-3 text-gray-300">Sublimity</td><td class="text-gray-400">Adapted from Longinus for written prose: greatness of conception, not merely elevated diction</td></tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-zinc-800"><td class="py-2 pr-3 text-gray-300">Sentence structure</td><td class="text-gray-400">First systematic treatment for English: unity, strength, clarity as structural properties</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="py-2 pr-3 text-gray-300">Criticism</td><td class="text-gray-400">Judgment as a skill to be developed, not a gift to be discovered</td></tr>
